            <who name="Fabian Jakobs">fabian.jakobs</who>
            <bug_when>2009-11-23 18:18:45 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>Fixed in r20752

The exception is gone but the empty menu still looks ugly.

- TableModel is no longer nullable.
- The constructor still allows a null value for the
  table model. In this case the model returned by
  &#39;getEmptyTableModel&#39; is used.
- To configure the table with an empty model after
  creation use &#39;table.setTableModel(table.getEmptyTableModel());&#39;

This is an application of the null object pattern</thetext>
